## Quality Filter (Promo Replies)

**Engagement floor: 20+ likes minimum for promo replies.** Prefer 50+ but 20+ OK when no better targets.

| Check | Rule |
|-------|------|
| Fresh | < 48h |
| **Engagement** | **20+ likes minimum** (prefer 50+) |
| Relevant | Matches brand angle ({{#each pillars}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}) |
| Crowded | Skip 100+ replies |
| Real | Skip bots, corps, farmers |
| Sweet spot | 50-200 likes, < 30 replies, < 12h = IDEAL promo target |

## Viral Detection

| Priority | Likes | Replies | Age | Action |
|----------|-------|---------|-----|--------|
| **Urgent** | **200+** | **< 50** | **< 12h** | **Reply immediately, top quality** |
| High | 100-200 | < 30 | < 6h | Reply ASAP, extra care |
| Medium | 50-100 | < 50 | < 12h | Good candidate |
| Acceptable | 20-50 | < 30 | < 48h | OK if no better targets |

500+ likes → consider quote tweet instead. Log "viral tweet".

## Strategic Replies (NEW - Growth Engine)

**Purpose:** Reply to 10K+ accounts with genuinely valuable insight. NO product mention. Goal: get seen by their large audience.

**Target accounts:** See `queries.json → target_accounts` (ai_dev, pm_leaders, productivity, founders)

**Discovery workflow:**
1. Use ONE advanced search covering all target accounts: `from:X OR from:Y OR from:Z min_faves:100`
2. If 0 results → skip. Do NOT fall back to profile-hopping or trending.
3. Pick best tweet (highest likes, relevant to our niche, < 50 replies)
4. Reply with expert-level insight, personal experience, or data

🚨 **NEVER navigate to individual profiles one-by-one** — wastes 3+ minutes when accounts haven't posted recently.

**Target account strategy:** Focus on 5K-50K follower accounts. Big celebrities (500K+) bury our replies among hundreds. Medium accounts = better reply visibility.

**Filter for strategic replies:**
| Check | Rule |
|-------|------|
| Account size | 5K-50K ideal (larger OK if < 50 replies) |
| Tweet engagement | 100+ likes minimum |
| Relevance | Must be in our niche ({{#each pillars}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}) |
| Crowded | < 50 replies (our reply still visible) |
| Fresh | < 24h |

**Voice:** Genuinely helpful. Expert insight. Personal experience. NO product mention. NO links. Just pure value.

**Update:** `daily.strategic_replies.current += 1` per reply. Log `Type: "Strategic Reply"`

## Retweets (NEW)

**Purpose:** Keep feed active, show engagement, amplify niche content.

**What to retweet:**
- Viral tweets in our niches ({{#each pillars}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}})
- Industry news relevant to {{brand_tagline}}
- Relatable content from our community
- Complementary tools (NOT competitors)
- Founder stories and building-in-public moments

**What NOT to retweet:**
- Direct competitors (unless adding value)
- Controversial/political content
- Low-engagement tweets (< 50 likes)
- Crypto/NFT/forex

**Execution:** Use `[data-testid="retweet"]` button → click "Repost" option
**Update:** `daily.retweets.current += 1`. Log `Type: "Retweet"`

## Hashtag Strategy (NEW)

**For original tweets only.** NEVER use hashtags in replies (looks spammy).

**Rules:**
- 2-3 hashtags per original tweet
- Place at END of tweet, not beginning
- Mix: 1 topic-specific + 1-2 generic
- Don't use same hashtags every tweet — rotate from pools
- Check `queries.json → hashtag_pools` for available hashtags

