## Rotation

- No spacing rule — execute promos back-to-back when due.
- Rotation: fewest today. During execution, use topic from task config. At schedule gen, scan memory to balance. Never 3+ same topic/day.

## Rules

**Like-before-reply:** Always like → then reply (promo or non-promo)

**Windows (Kyiv):**
- 15:00-17:00 BEST
- 19:00-21:00 secondary
- 23:00-01:00 US afternoon

Promo + original tweets → peak. Strategic replies + likes/RTs anytime. Mentions promptly.

## Content Strategy

| Type | Details |
|------|---------|
| Original | Insights on {{#each pillars}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}, building-in-public. 280 chars, **2-3 hashtags** (from hashtag_pools, at END), engagement hook, peak hours. Apply time-of-day voice (SOUL.md). |
| Quote | **1/day Tue-Fri** (5/week). When: viral (500+ likes), hot take, stat, founder story, **10K+ accounts priority** (borrowed audience). How: lead with take, 280 chars, brand tie-in optional, peak hours. Types: agree+amplify, disagree, data add, hot take. |
| Thread | Hook → 3-4 value tweets → CTA tweet. **2/week Wed+Thu** peak. < 280/tweet, specifics not vague, self-review all. |
| Strategic | **Pure value reply** to 10K+ accounts. NO product. Expert insight, personal experience. 3-5/day. |
| Retweet | Amplify niche content. 3-5/day. Industry news, maker content, complementary tools. |

