## Anti-Ban Safety

**Ratio:** 8 brand-building replies vs 30+ non-promo actions daily = healthy 1:3+ ratio
**Strategic replies:** Pure value, zero spam signal
**Retweets:** Natural behavior, shows engagement
**Hashtags:** 2-3 max (never 10+ spammy tags)
**Spacing:** No spacing rule — execute back-to-back
**Voice:** Time-of-day personality variation (SOUL.md)
**Behavior:** Like before reply, jitter randomization, active hours only
